{
  "stem": "1918.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 233.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and then when the Hungarian Jews were brought in, there was-- there was no room in the crematorium, so they built open fires with all kinds of wood.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you heard the crackling of the wood, and you saw the flames, and you heard the shrieks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- I was not right there, but I heard the shrieks, I saw the flames, and they were throwing the children in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as long as I live, I will never find out whether my sister was murdered that way, or whether she was taken to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they were-- trucks, big tractors came around and they lifted it, tilted it, and they tilted the children into the open fire.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at times, some stronger child might have want to climb out somehow, and Mengele and his cohorts were standing there and pushing them back with a stick.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Mind you, pushing them back with a stick because they wouldn't touch it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was dirty work to touch them and push them back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A stick they pushed them back with, back into the fire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother saw it, and I saw the flames, I heard the shrieks, I heard the crackling of the wood, in addition to what was oozing out of the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my brother just recently told me that I didn't have children for a number of years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, I must have been some distance away from it, but, you know, I still see the flames and I hear the crackling, burning of the wood.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And truly, in addition to the swirling, charcoal gray smoke oozing out of the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Human mind can conceive such a thing, somebody can design something like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
